Ok, how about I actually tell you something about me here? Give me a moment...
*Creator of '''[https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ZeJlMdIb2baw48701_RzrErzaiwqPSEh/edit?usp=sharing&ouid=115728836020691915561&rtpof=true&sd=true| All Challenges Pantlock Run]''' -> Do all regional achievements, as orderly as possible, before moving to next region. Yes, that includes ''shinies''. *Currently suffering with '''7C Poison''' -> Beat the game only catching Poison Pok√©mon.
